Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 05-24-2025

Alley-oop! respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile game application (“the App”). By using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

1. Data Collection

We do not collect any personal information from users.

The App stores the following data on your device only:

High scores

Achievements

This data is saved locally and is not shared with us or any third party.

2. Data Usage

The data stored on your device is used solely for the following purposes:

Tracking your high scores

Recording your progress and achievements

This ensures a personalized experience within the App.

3. Data Sharing

We do not collect, transmit, or share your data with any external parties.

4. Third-Party Services

This App uses Google Admob plugins to display advertisements

Ads are G rated and non-personalized

This app also has Google Play Services integration for tracking achievements and highscores

5. Children's Privacy

Our App is designed for general audiences and does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 years of age.

6. Your Rights

Since we do not collect or store personal data, there is no data for you to access, modify, or request deletion of.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If changes are made, we will update the “Effective Date” at the top of this page. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any updates.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: pixelpupsoftware@gmail.com
